{"type": "article", "id": 27493, "title": "喇叭音箱", "description": "", "date": "2016-05-30T07:04:28Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 18, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702145758KWytzunMlbAeD0JZ.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>          </p>\n<p>美国密尔沃基的家具公司 Fiddle + Hammer 一直都致力于用最好的素材制作出视觉与听觉上都能带给人享受的产品，最近他们就推出了这款巨大的音箱 <a href=\"http://fiddlehammer.com/#/bellaphoneno7/\">Bellaphone</a> 。它的特别之处在于采用回收来的龙舌兰和威士忌酒桶制成，使得音乐更加“醉人”。木材质的喇叭造型不仅起到了放大音乐的效果，看上去也很像是一个来自留声机时代的传家宝。起初，这个音箱是由公司的创办人，雕塑家兼小提琴家 Jordan Waraksa 设计来专门播放自己创作的音乐的，现在已经投入量产。如果需要订购的话可以通过<a href=\"http://fiddlehammer.com/\">官网</a>联系他们。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702145754IUFvONW2GZhgm064.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\" data-ratio=\"0.81662592\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021457550Krds4AvJgxqYLkl.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.80929095\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702145756hbxrTKIAweU6pyQH.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75794621\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021457573eZV1LQjb2nRHBd5.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.74938875\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n"}